<P>IT has the &s;ame Subject as the X P&s;alm; 'Tis a Pray<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> directed again&s;t the &s;ame wicked men. Comp<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters"> the 14th ver&s;e&mdash;with the fate of <HI>Antichri&s;t.</HI> Mat. XXIV. 17.</P>
