<P N="1">1 THE Heavens, they declare abroad &Verbar; Maje&s;ty of God; &Verbar; and the expa<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">|ing Firmament &Verbar; &s;hews forth His Han work. &Verbar;</P>
