<DIV2 N="57" TYPE="Psalm">
<HEAD><HI>PSALM LVII.</HI> To the Chief Mu&s;ician. Alta&s;chith. Mictam of David, when be fled from Saul in the Cave.</HEAD>
<P N="1">1 BE merciful to me, O God; &Verbar; Be merciful to me: &Verbar; Becau&s;e my Soul in Thee <HI>alone</HI> &Verbar; does place its confidence. &Verbar; Yea, I will make my refuge in &Verbar; the &s;hadow of thy wings &Verbar; until that the calamities &Verbar; &s;hall be well o|verpa&s;t. &Verbar;</P>
