<P N="10">10 For thy great mercy <HI>does extend</HI> &Verbar; unto the very Heav<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ns; &Verbar; and to the tender Clouds <HI>there does &Verbar; extend</HI> thy faithfulne&s;s. &Verbar;</P>
