<DIV2 N="58" TYPE="Psalm">
<HEAD><HI>PSALM LVIII.</HI> To the Chief Mu&s;ician. Alta&s;chith. Mictam of David.</HEAD>
<P N="1">1 DO ye indeed &s;peak Righetou&s;ne&s;s, &Verbar; O you confederate ones? &Verbar; Do ye judge <HI>none b<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"></HI> righteous things, &Verbar; O Sons of earth|ly Man! &Verbar;</P>
