<DIV2 N="105" TYPE="Psalm">
<HEAD>PSALM CV.</HEAD>
<P N="1">1 COnfe&s;s to the ETERNAL God, &Verbar; Call ye upon His Name; &Verbar; among the People O make known &Verbar; His admirable Works. &Verbar;</P>
<P N="2"><PB N="279" REF="001946_0316_0FFCB57D0F7D35C0">
2 To Him with voices &s;ing; to Him &Verbar; &s;ing too with In&s;truments; &Verbar; talk ye of all the wondrous Works &Verbar; which have been done by Him. &Verbar;</P>
<P N="3">3 Value your &s;elves upon the Name &Verbar; of His mo&s;t Holy One; &Verbar; O let the heart of them rejoyce &Verbar; who &s;eek th' ETERNAL God. &Verbar;</P>
<P N="4">4 O &s;eek ye the ETERNAL God, &Verbar; &s;eek ye His powerful &s;trength; &Verbar; Seek to behold His glorious Face, &Verbar; <HI>Do this</HI> continually. &Verbar;</P>
<P N="5">5 The admirable things which He &Verbar; hath done, Remember ye; &Verbar; the Prodigies which He has wrought &Verbar; and Judgments of His mouth &Verbar;</P>
