<HEAD>PSALM CVI.</HEAD>
<P N="1">1 <HI>SIng</HI> Hallelujah! O Confe&s;s &Verbar; to the ETER|NAL God; &Verbar; Becau&s;e that He is good; becau&s;e &Verbar; His mercy is forever. &Verbar;</P>
