<P N="3">3 Ble&s;&s;ed are they who do ob&s;erve &Verbar; the thing that's right-and-good; &Verbar; <HI>Ble&s;&s;ed is <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e</HI> who executes &Verbar; at all times righteou&s;ne&s;s. &Verbar;</P>
<P N="4">4 ETERNAL God, Remember me &Verbar; with &s;uch a favour as &Verbar; thou &s;how'&s;t thy People; <HI>and</HI> with thy &Verbar; Salvation vi&s;it me. &Verbar;</P>
