<P N="15">15 And the thing which they did reque&s;t &Verbar; He granted unto them; &Verbar; Neverthele&s;s <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> leanne&s;s He &Verbar; did &s;end into their Soul. &Verbar;</P>
<P N="16">16 Yea, and again&s;t Mo&s;es him&s;elf, &Verbar; they envy'd in the Camp; &Verbar; Again&s;t Aaron, the holy One &Verbar; of the ETERNAL God. &Verbar;</P>
<P N="17">17 The Earth did then open it&s;elf, &Verbar; and &s;wallow Dathan up; &Verbar; It overwhelm'd the Company &Verbar; which with Abiram were.</P>
