<P N="23">23 He then &s;aid, He'd de&s;troy them; but &Verbar; His cho&s;en Mo&s;es &s;tood &Verbar; <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> th' breach before Him to divert &Verbar; His wrath from &s;laying them. &Verbar;</P>
