<DIV2 N="109" TYPE="Psalm">
<HEAD><HI>PSALM CIX.</HI> To the Chief Mu&s;ician. A P&s;alm of David.</HEAD>
<P N="1">1 THou who art of my prai&s;e the God, &Verbar; O hold not thou thy Peace. &Verbar;</P>
<P N="2">For the mouth of the wicked One, &Verbar; ev'n the mouth of Deceit; &Verbar; the&s;e have wide open &s;et them&s;elves &Verbar; unto my prejudice; &Verbar; they have in talking with me us'd &Verbar; a Tongue of fal&s;ity. &Verbar;</P>
