<P>But we'll refer to the Common Annotations. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> take pious Mr <HI>Henry's,</HI> 'Abundance of <HI>Young</HI> O<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> 'verts, like drops of <HI>Dew</HI> in a Summer's Morning Or thus, <Q>From their very Childhood, thou ha&s;t<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters"> <HI>Dew</HI> of thy Peoples Youth: their Hearts and A&s;&s;<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters"> ons when they are Young.</Q></P>
